[vc_row][vc_column width=”1/2″][vc_column_text css=””]

asnu 42

The ASNU 42 fluid is a specially formulated calibration fluid for use with the ASNU Injector Diagnostic Testing & Servicing Systems. It is not suitable for use with any other equipment.

ASNU 42 is only available to order directly through ASNU and the official ASNU distributors and will require a confirmed ASNU machine registration to fulfil any orders.

Please contact ASNU HQ if you are in the UK or your nearest ASNU distributor if you are outside of the UK and wish to purchase any ASNU products.

Please Entre em contato if you wish to order the fluid or to acquire one of our market leading injector test benches.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=”1/2″][vc_single_image image=”3702″ img_size=”large” css=””][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row custom_css_code=”LmdlbS1idXR0b24tc2l6ZS1tZWRpdW0lN0IlMEElMjAlMjAlMjAlMjBtaW4td2lkdGglM0EyMjdweCUzQiUwQSUyMCUyMCUyMCUyMG1hcmdpbiUzQTIwcHglM0IlMEElN0Q=”][vc_column]
